{"tid":918061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：唯一的協議是中國必須開放自己的國家，以便允許美國展開競爭","createTime":"2018-11-27T01:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T05:02:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9921ab8738a36e234070b5a75c97196c3b493a","tid":918061,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20181127/s00010/399fbc6ff783ec924d046927f281dc14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20181127%2Fs00010%2F399fbc6ff783ec924d046927f281dc14.jpg&h=f4d0d0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》發布對美國總統特朗普的專訪，特朗普表示，如果在阿根廷召開的G20會議上無法與國定主席習近平達成協議，他準備對最後一批價值2670億美元的中國商品徵收關稅。特朗普說，稅率要麼是10%，也可能是25%。特朗普還表示，蘋果公司從中國進口的iPhone和筆記型電腦可能受到新關稅的打擊。他說，美國人可以「非常輕鬆地」應對10%的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普指，「唯一的協議是中國必須開放自己的國家，以便允許美國展開競爭。至於其它國家，這就取決於他們了。」。《華爾街日報》報道稱，中國官員表示，他們眼中兩國在G20的關鍵成果是說服美國推遲提高關稅。《華爾街日報》引述特朗普表示，美國不太可能接受北京提出的不上調關稅的要求。<br />\n<br />\n截至目前，蘋果最賺錢的產品，例如iPhone和iPad，都不在美國關稅清單之列，而Apple Watch和AirPods等一度受到影響，但之後美國表示不對此類產品徵稅。而蘋果在9月份警告說，其他產品，如Mac mini、Apple Pencil手寫筆以及一些電纜和外殼，可能受到打擊。受特朗普最新言論此影響，蘋果股價在收市後交易中下跌約1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1543278438474&amp;issue=20181127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1543278438474%26issue%3D20181127&d=JGgYy0LqdrBMYXb44KbCrr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ef6bf3c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1543278438474%26issue%3D20181127&h=b7b53c49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1543278438474&amp;issue=20181127</a>"},{"pid":"48047172003eb1f193ca82571fdd1ca43378d575","tid":918061,"uid":29080,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:19:47.000Z","msg":"船堅炮利怕你麼？"},{"pid":"320f08f7303a6ddec317d21fded5f83c290e81c8","tid":918061,"uid":152476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"開放市場<br />\n即係無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53d708b5035a618980f29e4017e68223134b6a2","tid":918061,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:37:29.000Z","msg":"怕什麼...<br />\n<br />\n中國人咁愛國,洋鬼佬黎賣野只會失敗"},{"pid":"f06fec9a9f912423c039f1169e81852b9891b838","tid":918061,"uid":138441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:41:15.000Z","msg":"打，往死裏打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b7864fd9f8e0e9a195645f5e09fab4491f0cda","tid":918061,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"邊可能開放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中共仲要用國企養一大班廢人"},{"pid":"4e87c61d487a6b5632de3e177417d5152d012b51","tid":918061,"uid":18251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"320f08f7303a6ddec317d21fded5f83c290e81c8","tid":918061,"uid":152476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"開放市場<br />\n即係無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"入嚟先玩死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821832c40843e3f8ee75bf3c80bf9050f74cad3c","tid":918061,"uid":153031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4990f6bfc09f6f36f019a75307cf60f22040644","tid":918061,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70463d6b927145b3833d467e01538d8e67969a77","tid":918061,"uid":51085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"門戶開放2.0"},{"pid":"336b857f63317cf61293e04a3089eefe94f4f3d3","tid":918061,"uid":51